caption.p: Supplementary Figure 1: numbers of HIV and HCV sequences available in Los Alamos Database are shown for each country. HCV Genotype 1b NS5B, HCV Genotype 3a NS5B, HIV Subtype A env, and HIV Subtype A gag are color-coded in boxes as yellow, green, light blue, and dark blue, respectively.
